[{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0053","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0053.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1601","title":"Joomla! JA Comment 组件 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 JA Comment（com_jacomment）组件存在目录遍历漏洞，其 index.php 在处理 view 参数时未对用户输入做充分校验与过滤。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需在请求 index.php 的 view 参数中构造包含 ..（点-点）的恶意路径序列，即可越权读取目标服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、源码、密码等敏感信息）。该漏洞影响所有安装了存在缺陷版本 JA Comment 组件的 Joomla! 站点，攻击条件仅需网络可达目标 Web 服务并发送特制 HTTP 请求即可，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级为中。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1601"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-29","updated":"2026-07-15","remediation":"建议立即升级 JA Comment 组件到官方发布的最新修复版本；若暂无法升级，可在后台扩展管理中停用或卸载 com_jacomment 组件以彻底消除风险。同时应在组件控制器中对 view 参数进行白名单校验，过滤 ../ 与空字节等非法字符，并在 Web 服务器层（如 Apache 的 .htaccess）限制对敏感路径参数的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlajacomment-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39472","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12236","http://www.osvdb.org/63802","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39516","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57848","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12236","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1601.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1601.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1601.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1601.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-1601-1737.yaml","https://github.com/1in9e/gosint/blob/bdda4461515c4398c08638676bbbfe451b73ff95/client/vuln_scan/nuclei/tools/nuclei-templates/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1601.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder5/cve-2010-1601-1736.yaml","https://github.com/patrickmpalmer/exploit-prediction-calculator/blob/a048424e68e6b5ea7f4d32bf29dddd4eda342b01/data_gathering/data/exploited_cves.csv","https://github.com/foreztgump/cve_json/blob/b5f345eafeb97dce3fe03de3869b187e0574a5c0/2010/CVE-2010-1601.json","https://github.com/amad3us47/amad3us47.github.io/blob/07cfc0edf465277028554b47198f6f186d3215b6/data/cve-2010-1601-1735.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-1601_2.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0053.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0052","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0052.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1586","title":"惠普系统管理主页 - 'RedirectUrl' 参数 URL 重定向漏洞","description":"惠普系统管理主页（System Management Homepage）是一款为服务器管理的IT管理员提供的综合工具，可预测、诊断和快速响应潜在或实际的系统故障。攻击者可通过SMH的可信URL漏洞利用RedirectUrl参数劫持受害者跳转到任意恶意网站，进而利用浏览器漏洞进一步攻击受害者操作系统并实现远程代码执行。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1586"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb","hp","nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-28","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到惠普系统管理主页v6.2或更高版本以修复漏洞，建议安装供应商发布的最新补丁和安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T11:00:54.047473758+00:00","references":["http://yehg.net/lab/pr0js/advisories/hp_system_management_homepage_url_redirection_abuse","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39676","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58107","http://h20000.www2.hp.com/bizsupport/TechSupport/Document.jsp?objectID=c02518794&lang=en&cc=us&taskId=101&prodSeriesId=344313&prodTypeId=18964","http://yehg.net/lab/pr0js/advisories/hp_system_management_homepage_url_redirection_abuse"],"poc_urls":["http://x.x.x.x:2301/red2301.html?RedirectUrl=evil@attacker.com"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0052.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0051","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0051.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1540","title":"Joomla! com_myblog 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! com_myblog 组件 3.0.329 版本的 index.php 存在目录遍历漏洞，远程未认证攻击者可通过 task 参数传入目录遍历序列（../）读取服务器任意文件。该漏洞源于对用户输入的 task 参数未进行路径规范化校验，攻击者可构造恶意路径遍历序列读取敏感系统文件（如 /etc/passwd、配置文件等），影响使用该组件的 Joomla! 站点，CVSS 评分 5.0（中危），属路径遍历类漏洞（CWE-22）。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1540"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb","nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-26","updated":"2026-07-15","remediation":"卸载存在目录遍历漏洞的 com_myblog 组件 3.0.329，替换为官方维护的安全替代组件；升级 Joomla! 至最新受支持版本；对 task 参数进行路径规范化校验，拒绝包含 '../' 或空字节编码的恶意输入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/38777","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11625","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/38530"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0051.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0075","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0075.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1955","title":"Joomla! Deluxe Blog Factory 组件本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! Deluxe Blog Factory 1.1.2 组件存在本地文件包含漏洞，攻击者可利用此漏洞读取服务器上的敏感文件，如/etc/passwd等。漏洞源于 improper input sanitization，允许攻击者通过目录遍历攻击读取任意文件，可能导致信息泄露或进一步系统入侵。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1955"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2010-04-15","updated":"2010-06-15","remediation":"升级 Joomla! 到最新版本（≥3.9.0），彻底修复受影响的 Deluxe Blog Factory 组件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T15:18:49.780232661+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2010-1955","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12868"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12868"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0075.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0116","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0116.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-5286","title":"Joomla! com_jstore 组件 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Jstore（com_jstore）第三方扩展组件存在目录遍历（路径遍历）漏洞，属于 CWE-22 类型缺陷。该组件在处理 index.php 页面的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤与规范化，远程攻击者可构造包含 \"..\"（点点）序列的恶意 controller 参数提交请求，绕过目录访问限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、密码等敏感数据）。由于该组件作为 Joomla! 站点插件部署，凡安装并启用了存在漏洞版本 com_jstore 组件的 Joomla! 网站均受影响。攻击者无需身份认证，仅需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，CVSS 基础评分高达 10.0（满分），危害等级为严重，除文件读取外还可能存在其他未明确说明的安全影响。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-5286"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2012-11-26T23:55:01.300","updated":"2026-06-16T23:26:28.973","remediation":"立即卸载或升级存在漏洞的 Jstore (com_jstore) 第三方组件至官方修复版本，并通过后台「扩展管理-管理」彻底移除该组件；若暂不能升级，可在 Web 服务器（如 Apache 的 .htaccess）中对 index.php 的 controller 参数做过滤，拒绝包含「../」「..%2f」等路径穿越字符的请求，同时配置 PHP 的 open_basedir 限制脚本可访问目录，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1010-exploits/joomlajstore-lfi.txt","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/44053","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/34837","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5286.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-5286.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5286.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e7bd0957d7eea7c21095268cca9721e428611ed/cves/2010/5xxx/CVE-2010-5286.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-5286-2032.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-5286-2031.yaml","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_iddirtra","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-5286-2034.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2010-5286_10.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/27/Artifact/Report.csv","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2010-5286-2034.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0116.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0115","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0115.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-5278","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9185,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10867}}","description":"MODx Revolution 2.0.2-pl 及更早版本的 manager/controllers/default/resource/tvs.php 文件存在路径遍历漏洞。当服务器 magic_quotes_gpc 配置被禁用时，程序未对 class_key 参数进行充分的过滤和校验，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过在该参数中注入 \"..\"（点点）序列绕过目录限制，从而读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、源代码等），造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞利用条件较为简单，攻击者只需构造包含目录遍历序列的恶意 HTTP 请求即可触发，CVSS 评分 4.3，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-2010-5278"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2012-10-07T20:55:00.907","updated":"2026-06-16T23:26:28.083","remediation":"建议立即升级 MODx Revolution 至 2.0.3 及以上版本，官方已在 2.0.3 版本修复该路径遍历漏洞。若暂时无法升级，可通过以下方式缓解：1) 在 php.ini 中开启 magic_quotes_gpc = On（PHP 5.4+ 已废弃）；2) 在 Web 服务器层面限制对 /manager/controllers/default/resource/tvs.php 的访问权限，仅允许受信 IP 访问后台管理目录；3) 部署 WAF 规则拦截包含 ../ 路径遍历载荷的 class_key 参数请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://modxcms.com/forums/index.php/topic%2C55104.0.html","http://modxcms.com/forums/index.php/topic%2C55105.msg317273.html","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1009-exploits/modx202pl-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/41638","http://www.johnleitch.net/Vulnerabilities/MODx.Revolution.2.0.2-pl.Local.File.Inclusion/49","http://www.osvdb.org/68265","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/43577","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/62073","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/34788","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5278.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-5278.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5278.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-5278.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-5278-2028.yaml","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-5278-2030.yaml","https://github.com/u21h2/nacs/blob/1eaa239ded7496317a47073605c8ddda70686ef5/web/poc/pocs/nuclei/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5278.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Apr/16/Reports/Report.csv","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/2010/CVE-2010-5278.md","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-5278_2.yaml","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2010/CVE-2010-5278.rules"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0115.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0114","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0114.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-5028","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9103,\"outputTokens\":25,\"totalTokens\":10856}}","description":"Joomla! JExtensions JE Job (com_jejob) 组件 1.0 版本的 index.php 文件中 item 操作的 catid 参数存在 SQL 注入漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 catid 参数传递特制的 SQL 语句，执行任意 SQL 命令，导致数据库信息泄露、数据篡改甚至服务器完全沦陷。该漏洞影响使用该组件的所有 Joomla! 站点，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，属高危漏洞。攻击者可构造恶意 catid 参数值（如 ' UNION SELECT ...）注入 SQL 语句，获取数据库敏感信息或写入 Webshell 进一步控制服务器。厂商已停止维护该组件，建议立即卸载或升级至安全版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-5028"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-11-02T21:55:16.997","updated":"2026-06-16T23:26:00.103","remediation":"立即升级或卸载存在漏洞的 Harmistechnology JE Job (com_jejob) 1.0 组件，替换为官方已修复版本或停用该组件。临时缓解措施：在 Joomla 后台禁用 com_jejob 组件，并通过 Web 应用防火墙对 index.php 的 catid 参数做 SQL 注入过滤与输入校验，限制远程匿名访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/39837","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12782","http://www.osvdb.org/64708","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/40193","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1269","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58599","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12601","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5028.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-5028.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5028.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-5028.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-5028-2021.yaml","https://github.com/masahiro331/nvd-list/blob/4937ab886b2d99e2047bc7eafc242f2653ee7558/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5028.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-5028_24.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2010/CVE-2010-5028.json","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2010/README.md","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2010-5028-2023.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Mar/19/Reports/lfiReport.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0114.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0113","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0113.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4977","title":"Miniwork Com Canteen 1.0 SQL注入漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Canteen（com_canteen）组件 1.0 版本在 menu.php 中存在 SQL 注入漏洞。该组件在处理用户请求时未对传入 index.php 的 mealid 参数进行严格的输入校验与转义，导致攻击者可通过构造恶意的 SQL 语句拼接至数据库查询中。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用该参数执行任意 SQL 命令，进而读取、篡改或删除数据库中的敏感数据，甚至在特定配置下进一步获取系统权限。该漏洞影响所有安装了 Canteen 1.0 组件的 Joomla! 站点，攻击条件仅需目标站点对外开放 Web 服务且存在该缺陷组件，利用方式简单，危害等级较高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4977"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-11-01T22:55:04.023","updated":"2026-06-16T23:25:54.267","remediation":"由于 Joomla! Canteen (com_canteen) 组件 1.0 存在 SQL 注入漏洞且厂商已停止维护，建议立即从 Joomla! 后台卸载并彻底删除该扩展。若业务必须使用，应在代码中对 index.php 传入的 mealid 参数强制类型转换为整型（intval）并使用参数化查询/预处理语句，同时部署 WAF 拦截含 SQL 关键字的恶意请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/66031","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1007-exploits/joomlacanteen-lfisql.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/40503","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/8495","http://www.salvatorefresta.net/files/adv/Canteen%20Joomla%20Component%201.0%20Multiple%20Remote%20Vulnerabilities-04072010.txt","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/512170/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/41358","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/60103","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/34250","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4977.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4977.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4977.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-4977.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-4977-2019.yaml","https://github.com/w4n95/vuls-data-raw-exploit-inthewild/blob/2c8c2568a21a9cc77244882f65c37bca47d71613/2010/CVE-2010-4977.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-4977_40.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/27/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-4977-2018.yaml","https://github.com/chessredoffsec/nuclei-templates/blob/bf798045b1c57839b4998bf6e08c74fbfd076879/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4977.yaml","https://github.com/wpsec/ARL-Source-Install/blob/aecf83f1f55a6f1a1a67dbe25e22ea0eb5a44bf2/tools/nuclei-templates/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4977.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0113.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0112","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0112.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4769","title":"Janguo Jimtawl 组件 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Jimtawl（com_jimtawl）组件 1.0.2 存在目录遍历（路径遍历）漏洞，根源在于其对用户传入的 `task` 参数未做充分的路径安全校验，未过滤 `../`（点点）序列。远程攻击者在无需身份认证的情况下，可向 `index.php` 的 `task` 参数注入包含 `../` 的恶意路径，从而跨越 Web 根目录读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、密码文件等敏感信息），并可能借此造成其他未明确说明的安全影响。该漏洞影响运行 Joomla! 并安装了 Jimtawl 1.0.2 组件的网站，攻击条件仅为目标站点存在该脆弱组件且可直接访问前端入口，利用方式简单，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4769"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-03-23T22:00:01.683","updated":"2026-06-16T23:25:30.723","remediation":"立即升级或卸载存在漏洞的 Janguo Jimtawl (com_jimtawl) 1.0.2 组件，改用官方已修复的版本；若暂无法升级，请登录 Joomla! 后台在「扩展管理」中禁用或移除该组件，并在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）配置中拒绝 index.php 中 task 参数包含 `../` 序列的请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/42324","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15585","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/44992","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15585","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4769.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4769.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4769.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fcc97d3f09074a6534df65087e2097c6145b988b/cves/2010/4xxx/CVE-2010-4769.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-4769-2013.yaml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2010/CVE-2010-4769.md","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2010-4769_1.yaml","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-4769-2013.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2010-4769-2012.yaml","https://github.com/patrickmpalmer/exploit-prediction-calculator/blob/a048424e68e6b5ea7f4d32bf29dddd4eda342b01/data_gathering/data/exploited_cves.csv","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-4769-2014.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0112.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0111","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0111.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4719","title":"Fxwebdesign Com Jradio 路径遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 平台的 Fxwebdesign JRadio（com_jradio）组件在 1.5.1 之前版本中存在目录遍历漏洞。该组件在处理 index.php 的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤与校验，导致远程攻击者可在 controller 参数中插入\"../\"等目录遍历序列，从而突破 Web 根目录限制，读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、敏感源码等）。攻击无需身份认证，仅需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，影响所有运行受影响版本 JRadio 组件的 Joomla! 站点，可能导致敏感信息泄露，进而为进一步的入侵提供条件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4719"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-02-01T23:00:03.437","updated":"2026-06-16T23:25:24.880","remediation":"建议将 Joomla! 的 JRadio (com_jradio) 组件升级至 1.5.1 或更高版本，可从官方扩展目录重新下载安装以覆盖存在漏洞的旧版。若无法立即升级，可在 Joomla! 后台禁用或卸载 com_jradio 组件，并通过 Web 服务器规则（如 Apache 的 .htaccess）拒绝对外界暴露 index.php 中 controller 参数的非预期目录遍历字符（../ 等），作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/files/view/96751/joomlajradio-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/42600","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15749","http://www.fxwebdesign.nl/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=20&Itemid=56","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/45440","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/64143","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15749","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4719.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4719.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4719.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-4719.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-4719-2009.yaml","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-4719-2007.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-4719_23.yaml","https://github.com/1in9e/gosint/blob/bdda4461515c4398c08638676bbbfe451b73ff95/client/vuln_scan/nuclei/tools/nuclei-templates/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4719.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-4719_3.yaml","https://github.com/masahiro331/nvd-list/blob/4937ab886b2d99e2047bc7eafc242f2653ee7558/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4719.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-4719_21.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0111.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0110","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0110.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4617","title":"Joomla! JotLoader 组件 目录遍历本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 JotLoader（com_jotloader）组件 2.2.1 版本存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞。该组件在处理 index.php 的 section 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤与校验，远程攻击者可在该参数中插入 \"../\" 等目录遍历序列，从而读取目标服务器上任意文件（如配置文件、敏感源码等）。攻击无需身份认证，仅需向受影响站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，影响所有运行 JotLoader 2.2.1 的 Joomla! 站点，可能导致敏感信息泄露与进一步入侵。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4617"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-12-29T22:33:32.633","updated":"2026-06-16T23:25:11.130","remediation":"建议立即将 JotLoader 组件升级至官方发布的 2.2.2 或更高版本（修复了 section 参数的目录遍历过滤）。若暂无法升级，可在 Joomla 后台禁用或卸载 com_jotloader 组件，并在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）配置中通过 mod_security 规则拦截包含 ../ 及 null 字节的 section 参数请求，同时在 php.ini 中设置 open_basedir 限制文件访问范围作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/files/view/96812/joomlajotloader-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15791","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/64223","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15791","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4617.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4617.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4617.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fcc97d3f09074a6534df65087e2097c6145b988b/cves/2010/4xxx/CVE-2010-4617.json","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-4617-2006.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-4617.js","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-4617_17.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2010-4617-2004.yaml","https://github.com/rjp2525/cve-data/blob/2f3ce5ef3a11f37d0a2e7d88f12b74499612a438/2010/CVE-2010-4617.json","https://github.com/ByteLobo/joomla/blob/32cae09fae17c01b9f6627cf8f2fb46045643162/templatesfuncional/CVE-2010-4617.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/z-11753.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0110.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0109","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0109.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4282","title":"Pandora FMS 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Pandora FMS 在 3.1.1 版本之前存在多个目录遍历漏洞（CWE-22）。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 ajax.php 的 page 参数、general/pandora_help.php 的 id 参数，或 operation/agentes/networkmap.php 的 layout 参数传入包含 \"../\" 等路径遍历序列的特制请求，利用 PHP 本地文件包含机制读取、包含并执行服务器上的任意本地文件。其中 networkmap.php 的 layout 参数更可被滥用来创建、修改或删除任意本地文件。该漏洞影响所有 3.1.1 之前的 Pandora FMS 版本，攻击仅需网络访问 Web 接口即可发起，无需登录凭证，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4282"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-12-02T17:15:00.597","updated":"2026-06-16T23:24:30.327","remediation":"建议立即升级 Pandora FMS 至 3.1.1 或更高版本。若暂时无法升级，可在 Web 应用防火墙配置规则拦截包含目录遍历序列（如 ../）的 page、id、layout 参数请求，并限制 ajax.php、pandora_help.php、networkmap.php 的访问权限为仅可信 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/69543","http://osvdb.org/69544","http://osvdb.org/69545","http://seclists.org/fulldisclosure/2010/Nov/326","http://secunia.com/advisories/42347","http://sourceforge.net/projects/pandora/files/Pandora%20FMS%203.1/Final%20version%20%28Stable%29/pandorafms_console-3.1_security_patch_13Oct2010.tar.gz/download","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15643","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/514939/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/45112","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4282.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4282.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4282.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-4282.js","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-4282-2001_1.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-4282-1999.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder5/cve-2010-4282-2002.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-4282_4.yaml","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/35fe940be4a8cc841207d0ee607b7714e4ad436d/2010/CVE-2010-4282.json","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/20/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-4282_25.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0109.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0109.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0108","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0108.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4239","title":"Tiki Wiki CMS Groupware 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Tiki Wiki CMS Groupware 5.2 版本存在本地文件包含漏洞，攻击者可通过构造恶意文件路径参数，利用输入验证不当缺陷包含本地任意文件，进而读取敏感文件或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Tiki Wiki CMS Groupware 5.2 版本，CVSS 评分 9.8（CRITICAL），攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，通过构造恶意文件包含路径实现任意代码执行或敏感文件读取，危害等级严重。官方已发布补丁修复该漏洞，建议用户尽快升级到修复版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4239"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2019-10-28T15:15:12.583","updated":"2026-06-16T23:24:25.063","remediation":"tags.<value>建议立即升级至 Tiki Wiki CMS Groupware 5.3 或更高版本（官方已在 5.3 修复该 LFI 漏洞）。若暂时无法升级，可在 Web 服务器层面限制对 tiki-print_multi_pages.php 等受影响脚本的访问，并配置 PHP 的 open_basedir 限制文件包含路径；同时在防火墙层面封禁可疑请求参数（如 page、lang 等）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["https://access.redhat.com/security/cve/cve-2010-4239","https://dl.packetstormsecurity.net/1009-exploits/tikiwiki52-lfi.txt","https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2010-4239","https://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2010/11/22/9","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4239.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4239.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4239.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/04deea2d5c50b4720e70811dcb426620621d3261/cves/2010/4xxx/CVE-2010-4239.json","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder1/cve-2010-4239-1997.yaml","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/bf9978ea592b7413bb96dfeb9db92cbd52bf0c3d/api/2010/CVE-2010-4239.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/cve-2010-4239.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/yaml/Tiki%20Wiki%20CMS/CVE-2010-4239.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-4239_3.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-2010-4239_2_1.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2010-4239-1997.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0108.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0104","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0104.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-3426","title":"Joomla! Jphone 组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! JPhone 组件 1.0 Alpha 3 版本的 jphone.php 文件存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 index.php 的 controller 参数传入 ../ 目录遍历序列，包含并执行服务器上的任意本地文件。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 使用 JPhone 组件 1.0 Alpha 3 版本的站点，CVSS 评分 7.5（高危），属于 CWE-22 路径遍历类型。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，通过构造恶意 controller 参数实现本地文件包含，进而可能导致敏感文件读取或代码执行。ExploitDB 已公开相关利用代码。Joomla! 官方已发布更新版本修复该漏洞，建议升级至修复版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-3426"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-09-16T22:00:03.267","updated":"2026-06-16T23:22:44.687","remediation":"立即卸载或禁用 Joomla! 站点中已停更的 JPhone (com_jphone) 1.0 Alpha 3 组件（后台「扩展-管理」中卸载），并删除 /components/com_jphone 与 /modules 下相关文件。若必须保留，应升级到官方后续修复版本或在 jphone.php 中对 controller 参数使用 basename() 过滤并限制白名单，同时在 .htaccess 中拒绝含 \"..\" 的请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1009-exploits/joomlajphone-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14964","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/43147","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/61723","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14964","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-3426.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-3426.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-3426.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-3426.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-3426-1992.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-3426-1990.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-3426_12.yaml","https://github.com/youki992/VscanPlus/blob/714a0e276a538a22c1a6215c71458a8b59a920ef/pocs_yml/nucleiFiles/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-3426.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2010-3426-1992.yaml","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/2010/CVE-2010-3426.json","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/20/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0104.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0103","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0103.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-3203","title":"Joomla! PicSell 组件 目录遍历任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 PicSell（com_picsell）组件 1.0 版本存在目录遍历漏洞（CWE-22）。该组件在处理 index.php 的 prevsell dwnfree 动作时，未对 dflink 参数进行充分的路径过滤与校验，攻击者可构造包含 \"../\"（点-点-斜杠）序列的恶意参数值，突破 Web 根目录限制，实现任意文件读取。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发该漏洞，从而读取服务器上的敏感文件（如配置文件、源码、口令文件等），可能导致信息泄露乃至进一步渗透。受影响范围为安装了 PicSell 1.0 组件且未打补丁的 Joomla! 站点。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-3203"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-09-03T18:00:02.577","updated":"2026-06-16T23:22:22.070","remediation":"建议立即升级 Joomla! 至 1.5.22 或更高版本，并卸载或禁用 PicSell (com_picsell) 1.0 组件；若无法升级，请在 Web 应用防火墙配置规则拦截包含 ../ 的 dflink 参数请求，并限制 Web 服务器进程对敏感目录的读取权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/41187","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14845","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14845","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-3203.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-3203.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-3203.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bb86e46de27f177abd11211a1c508ec72b4b0dea/cves/2010/3xxx/CVE-2010-3203.json","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-3203-1988.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-3203-1986_3.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-3203_6.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/2010/3xxx/CVE-2010-3203.json","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Jan/22/Reports/Report.csv","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-3203-